          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Support Local Transportation Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises requirements for the surface transportation block grant program to increase the percentages of program funds required to be allocated to states for each of FY2018-FY2020 for surface transportation projects in:</p> <ul> <li>urbanized areas with a population of over 200,000,</li> <li>non-urban areas with a population greater than 5,000, and</li> <li>other areas of the state.</li> </ul>]]></text>
